      "value": "<em>Yours small stature helps you avoid ranged attacks.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Dex 13, Small size or smaller.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You gain a +1 dodge bonus to AC against ranged attacks. In addition, you do not provide soft cover to creatures when ranged attacks pass through your square.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When targeted by a ranged attack, you can spend a number of stamina points up to your Dexterity bonus. For each stamina point you spend in this way, your dodge bonus to AC against that attack increases by 1.",
